text: Maria Dzieża (born 26 May 1949) is a Polish rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lesser Poland Voivodeship
